v0.7.0
After looong absence:
- disabled sailjail sandboxing
- fixed the change in cookies database (baseDomain --> host), hereby
- fixed the empty cookies and configuration lists
- adapted to renaming of aliendalvik to appsupport
- added support for community ports (decrypt-home_encrypted.service)
